@startuml
actor Utilisateur
participant "Esidom front-end" as FrontEnd
participant "Esidom back-end" as BackEnd
participant "Home Assistant" as HomeAssistant

Utilisateur -> FrontEnd: Lister les routines
FrontEnd -> BackEnd: GET /automations
BackEnd -> HomeAssistant: WS: {type: "get_states"}
HomeAssistant --> BackEnd: WS: {type: "result", success: true, result: []}
BackEnd --> FrontEnd: 200 - Ok
FrontEnd --> Utilisateur: Les routines sont listées
@enduml
